Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.83,0:00:17.93,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur16\fad(400,400)}小さな思い出たち
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.13,0:00:23.43,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur16\fad(400,400)}両手いっぱい抱えて
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.73,0:00:28.83,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur16\fad(400,400)}あなただけ 想ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.23,0:00:34.33,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur16\fad(400,400)}そんな時間(とき)がうれしい
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.33,0:00:39.93,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur16\fad(400,400)}どんなに離れても
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.83,0:00:45.73,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur16\fad(400,400)}愛する気持ちはいつでも
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.33,0:00:51.23,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur16\fad(400,400)}あなたの隣にそっと
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.03,0:00:57.93,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur16\fad(400,400)}寄り添っている
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.23,0:01:05.13,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur16\fad(400,400)}そう 決して終わることのない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.83,0:01:10.83,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur16\fad(400,400)}本当の愛 見つけたから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.33,0:01:16.23,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur16\fad(400,400)}「ずっとずっとそばにいます」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.73,0:01:21.83,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur16\fad(400,400)}誓ったあおい空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.86,0:01:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi Mon Dad
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.97,0:01:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi Tina
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.19,0:01:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You can take a tea break with a sweet
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.80,0:01:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes，Mom
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.79,0:01:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Tina!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.99,0:02:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,吓了我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.02,0:02:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 你这孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.57,0:02:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,最终话 ～绊～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.80,0:02:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你在看书啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.23,0:02:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,还以为你在玩游戏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.77,0:02:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,因为 蒂娜姐姐不在 一个人玩太无聊了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.96,0:02:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.31,0:02:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,最近打扫也很轻松呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.34,0:02:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,因为没有乱扔东西的人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.26,0:02:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.22,0:02:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,到底要什么时候才回来呀 蒂娜姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.50,0:03:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,薰少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.58,0:03:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,薰少爷 这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.74,0:03:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,蒂娜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.62,0:03:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,房东小姐 不好意思 郁女就麻烦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.30,0:03:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,难得回去一次 必须多孝敬孝敬父母
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.69,0:03:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,也许会待长点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.12,0:03:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,薰少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.66,0:03:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,蒂娜小姐她…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.91,0:03:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,会回来的 不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.18,0:03:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,蒂娜小姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.41,0:03:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,小葵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.83,0:04:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,薰少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.42,0:04:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,腌菜？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.47,0:04:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.57,0:04:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,新鲜的萝卜上市了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.00,0:04:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.37,0:04:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,因为蒂娜小姐最喜欢腌圆萝卜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.04,0:04:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,已经3个月了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.55,0:04:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,都快到蒂娜小姐的毕业典礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.70,0:04:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.40,0:04:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.77,0:04:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,还是联络一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.94,0:04:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,直接问问蒂娜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.48,0:04:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,失败失败
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.02,0:04:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,还真是难啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.18,0:05:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,再来挑战一次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.45,0:05:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.88,0:05:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,薰少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.61,0:05:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,给她家打电话
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.32,0:05:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 电话号码…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.77,0:05:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,去蒂娜的房间看看也许能知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.97,0:05:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然擅自进去有点过意不去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.60,0:05:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,蒂娜小姐 打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.52,0:05:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.58,0:06:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,薰少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.23,0:06:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,薰少爷 这到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.26,0:06:08.86,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.79,0:06:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,把回忆都留在这里了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.33,0:06:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,小葵 蒂娜也许不会再回到这里来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.52,0:06:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不会再回来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.53,0:06:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,蒂娜小姐不会再…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.84,0:06:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.87,0:06:35.34,Default,,0,0,0,,骗人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.82,0:06:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,这种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.31,0:06:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,这种事…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.85,0:06:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,蒂娜
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.30,0:06:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.14,0:07:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,正是吃的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.31,0:07:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 剩下我来做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.86,0:07:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.95,0:07:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啊 我真是的 还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.90,0:08:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.73,0:08:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我都忘了酱油用完了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.08,0:08:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,现在去买
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.51,0:08:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,小葵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.46,0:08:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.28,0:08:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.13,0:08:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,阿雅小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.50,0:08:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,今天也是和式饭菜吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.12,0:08:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.43,0:08:32.52,Default,,0,0,0,,葵小姐说要做好蒂娜学长\N什么时候回来都没问题的准备
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.02,0:08:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.47,0:08:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,毕业典礼是什么时候？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.91,0:08:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,大学的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.82,0:08:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,是后天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.09,0:08:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,糟糕 蒂娜学长不会是忘了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.95,0:08:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,后天…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.99,0:08:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,或者是不准备出席典礼了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.53,0:08:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不知道啊 话说回来…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.52,0:08:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,溢出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.43,0:09:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,烫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.86,0:09:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,烫烫烫烫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.48,0:09:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,就算蒂娜不在 也够热闹的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.79,0:09:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,好烫啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.00,0:09:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,很拿手嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.98,0:09:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,过奖了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.49,0:09:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,能也为我做一个吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.96,0:09:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.86,0:09:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,那么等这个做完
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.38,0:09:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,这个放到以后再做
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.83,0:09:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,又不知道那个人什么时候回来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.48,0:09:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.10,0:09:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.50,0:09:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,回美国以后竟然连个联络都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.95,0:09:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,也不想想大家多寂寞呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.39,0:09:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,小茧姐姐也寂寞吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.54,0:09:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.00,0:09:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,千香不就是因为寂寞才做布娃娃的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.74,0:09:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,小茧姐姐其实是很喜欢蒂娜姐姐的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.02,0:09:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.84,0:10:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,才 才不是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.85,0:10:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,谁会对那种野兽女人…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.57,0:10:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,布娃娃是无辜的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.62,0:10:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,吓了我一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.39,0:10:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,小葵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.65,0:10:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,是 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.86,0:10:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,有点走神了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.82,0:10:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,能陪我一会儿吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.19,0:10:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,很漂亮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.73,0:10:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是蒂娜最喜欢的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.43,0:10:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,说是和美国的景色很像
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.21,0:11:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,在那之后 我考虑过
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.01,0:11:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,关于蒂娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.63,0:11:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,她是没能说出口
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.33,0:11:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,因为太温柔了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.58,0:11:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,如果留在美国对于\N以后的蒂娜来说是件好事的话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.92,0:11:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要支持她
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.79,0:11:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,蒂娜小姐的将来…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.01,0:11:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.23,0:11:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.51,0:11:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,也要对大家说说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.00,0:11:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,蒂娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.82,0:11:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,蒂娜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.75,0:11:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我回来咯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.86,0:11:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,是蒂娜姐姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.86,0:11:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎回来！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.35,0:12:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,哇！千香
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.24,0:12:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,钿女也好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.98,0:12:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,什么嘛 回来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.39,0:12:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,难得这么平静
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.61,0:12:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,什么意思 你这小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.96,0:12:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,隔了这么久 再让我好好地…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.55,0:12:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,蒂娜小姐 安静点！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.87,0:12:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.81,0:12:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,房东小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.94,0:12:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,蒂娜小姐 要喝茶吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.10,0:12:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,喝茶？在这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.01,0:12:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,对 偶尔…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.11,0:13:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 房东小姐还真是乱来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.20,0:13:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.12,0:13:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,给你添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.39,0:13:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,真好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.08,0:13:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,还是房东小姐泡的茶最好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.08,0:13:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.38,0:13:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,可以的话 作为茶点 请尝尝这个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.05,0:13:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,噢 圆萝卜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.31,0:13:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.71,0:13:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.27,0:13:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.68,0:13:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,本来是打算昨晚拿出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.12,0:13:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,因为「欢迎回家PARTY」太闹了 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.62,0:14:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,昨晚太开心了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.67,0:14:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.65,0:14:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,蒂娜姐姐去哪里了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.78,0:14:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,难得夏树和千鹤来看她
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.40,0:14:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,会不会出去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.76,0:14:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,说过今天一天都在的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.53,0:14:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,去2楼找找看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.47,0:14:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,那个是？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.02,0:14:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,又在看啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.53,0:14:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,又是这个夸张的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.65,0:14:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,因为没这样穿过
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.61,0:14:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我的高中是穿和式裙裤的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.21,0:14:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,和式裙裤？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.53,0:14:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,真不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.20,0:14:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我也很中意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.92,0:14:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我要是和房东小姐在一个学校的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.99,0:15:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,也会稍微变得像房东小姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.12,0:15:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,因为房东小姐是我的憧憬
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.41,0:15:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,憧憬？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.70,0:15:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,又温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.06,0:15:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,又能干
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.80,0:15:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉像是女人中的女人\N（大和抚子）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.05,0:15:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,自从遇到房东小姐后
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.77,0:15:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直想成为一个像房东小姐一样的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.43,0:15:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,蒂娜小姐吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.13,0:15:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,当然咯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.62,0:15:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然没有说出来 但一直是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.38,0:15:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,不过我确实是够粗枝大叶的…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.40,0:15:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,不 不是那个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.66,0:15:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,和蒂娜小姐比的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.17,0:15:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,我…其实一直都很羡慕蒂娜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.48,0:15:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,蒂娜小姐有很多我所没有的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.40,0:15:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,行动力又强
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.09,0:15:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,无论何时 无论是谁 都能让他高兴起来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.18,0:16:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我每天都想 即使一点点\N蒂娜小姐的优点能分些给我的话就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.09,0:16:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗 一直都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.73,0:16:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,房东小姐竟然会这么想呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.62,0:16:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是一直不知道蒂娜小姐是这么看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.84,0:16:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,找到了 蒂娜姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.43,0:16:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,好像在笑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.98,0:16:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,两人的关系真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.13,0:16:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,小葵姐姐和蒂娜姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.46,0:16:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,关系非常好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.13,0:16:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.47,0:16:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,明天是毕业典礼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.69,0:16:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.09,0:16:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,可以的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.21,0:17:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,蒂娜姐姐好漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.41,0:17:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,很适合你呢 学长
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.17,0:17:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,还真是人靠衣装啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.70,0:17:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,什么！？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.34,0:17:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,想干架？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.62,0:17:13.14,Default,,0,0,0,,我可奉陪到底哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.73,0:17:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,今天被说什么都不生气
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.33,0:17:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 房东小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.27,0:17:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这是最棒的毕业典礼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.51,0:17:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,今天的感受 一生都不会忘记
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.28,0:17:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,蒂娜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.69,0:17:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,蒂娜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.16,0:17:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我本来是不准备回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.47,0:17:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,蒂娜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.89,0:17:53.16,Default,,0,0,0,,回到美国后
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.88,0:17:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸妈妈都非常开心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.94,0:17:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,所以想 这样过下去也不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.77,0:18:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.49,0:18:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然喜欢爸爸妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.85,0:18:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,但也喜欢房东小姐和薰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.16,0:18:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢大家
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.08,0:18:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 仔细考虑后…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.71,0:18:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,仔细考虑后…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.63,0:18:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.17,0:18:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,回到这里来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.79,0:18:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,这里会接受我的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.95,0:19:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,这里的话 我能以我的方式生活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.12,0:19:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,这里的话 我能找到未来的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.14,0:19:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是这么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.63,0:19:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,蒂娜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.45,0:19:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,蒂娜小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.44,0:19:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,果然 这里是特别的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.99,0:19:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢这里 喜欢大家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.96,0:19:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.13,0:19:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然对你们两个是件麻烦事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.64,0:19:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎回家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.40,0:19:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎回家 蒂娜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.77,0:19:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,房东小姐 薰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.30,0:19:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.51,0:19:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.04,0:19:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.79,0:20:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,薰少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.01,0:20:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都在这栋房子里生活
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.01,0:20:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,然后踏上旅程
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.29,0:20:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,时间不会停止
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.32,0:20:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,就算有一天会结束
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.06,0:20:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.89,0:20:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,和大家一起渡过的美好时光永远都不会消失
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.81,0:20:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,小葵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.74,0:20:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我会珍惜现在的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.52,0:20:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,从心底感谢这由缘分而来的相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.93,0:20:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.67,0:20:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,都靠这份缘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.46,0:20:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,才有现在的我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.66,0:20:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,因为有小葵以及大家在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.40,0:20:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.48,0:20:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,薰少爷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.01,0:20:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,要努力才行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.69,0:20:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我也必须在这里找到将来的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.43,0:20:54.91,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.06,0:20:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,有大家在的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.39,0:20:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,这个地方
